00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,780 --> 00:01:40,910
[Her Fantastic Adventures]

3
00:02:03,070 --> 00:02:04,990
Is anybody here?

4
00:02:06,350 --> 00:02:08,860
I'm Duan Yu from the Duan family of Changqing.

5
00:02:08,860 --> 00:02:13,060
I'm here to discuss something important with
the Lord of the Divine Palace.

6
00:02:15,910 --> 00:02:16,910
Strange?

7
00:02:17,870 --> 00:02:19,390
Why is it so quiet here?

8
00:02:28,590 --> 00:02:31,120
May I ask who you are?

9
00:02:31,740 --> 00:02:34,000
I'm Duan Yu. I have His Lordship's order.

10
00:02:34,030 --> 00:02:36,820
I came to discuss something important
with The Lord.

11
00:02:36,820 --> 00:02:37,750
I'd appreciate

12
00:02:38,870 --> 00:02:40,200
if you could inform him.

13
00:02:41,220 --> 00:02:43,800
[Episode 10]

14
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:50,900
Are you still upset about what happened
during the day?

15
00:03:50,900 --> 00:03:51,900
My Lady.

16
00:03:52,380 --> 00:03:52,970
I...

17
00:03:57,329 --> 00:03:59,090
I got you into trouble, My Lady.

18
00:04:01,190 --> 00:04:02,460
Silly girl.

19
00:04:03,230 --> 00:04:04,790
What are you talking about?

20
00:04:05,470 --> 00:04:08,550
I'm really happy that I can help.

21
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:11,550
It was my fault in the past.

22
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:14,470
I didn't realize what you were going through.

23
00:04:14,470 --> 00:04:15,970
If something like this happens again,

24
00:04:15,970 --> 00:04:17,630
you shouldn't keep it from me.

25
00:04:21,870 --> 00:04:22,800
Go ahead and cry.

26
00:04:23,670 --> 00:04:25,990
You'll feel better if you cry.

27
00:04:30,510 --> 00:04:31,670
My Lady,

28
00:04:33,230 --> 00:04:35,750
I also knew that

29
00:04:35,770 --> 00:04:37,970
the family's debt was paid off long ago.

30
00:04:38,860 --> 00:04:41,060
But he is my father.

31
00:04:41,890 --> 00:04:43,970
What else can I do?

32
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:45,680
Some people

33
00:04:45,870 --> 00:04:48,080
may be family,

34
00:04:48,590 --> 00:04:50,790
but they are actually obstacles.

35
00:04:51,220 --> 00:04:52,820
Don't be too sad.

36
00:04:53,540 --> 00:04:56,450
Considering my father did his best to help

37
00:04:57,070 --> 00:04:59,360
my mother recover from her illness,

38
00:05:00,510 --> 00:05:03,710
I'll think of it as a favour for my mother.

39
00:05:03,980 --> 00:05:04,750
Dongxi.

40
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,710
You are such a kind girl.

41
00:05:07,390 --> 00:05:08,380
You're on the ball.

42
00:05:08,380 --> 00:05:09,780
You have empathy and kindness.

43
00:05:09,780 --> 00:05:10,610
However,

44
00:05:10,990 --> 00:05:13,350
you don't have to be too upset

45
00:05:13,390 --> 00:05:15,150
for a nobody who's irrelevant to you.

46
00:05:15,150 --> 00:05:16,950
You should cherish the present,

47
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,460
and the people around you.

48
00:05:20,440 --> 00:05:22,570
I know you are kind to me.

49
00:05:22,820 --> 00:05:24,950
I will repay you for all your kindness.

50
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,260
Silly girl.

51
00:05:27,430 --> 00:05:28,830
I'm not talking about me.

52
00:05:29,250 --> 00:05:31,570
I meant Da.

53
00:05:35,510 --> 00:05:36,230
Who?

54
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:45,970
Da is such a loyal man.

55
00:05:47,150 --> 00:05:47,710
Look.

56
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,730
These earrings are beautiful.

57
00:05:49,870 --> 00:05:51,490
Da has good taste.

58
00:05:52,370 --> 00:05:54,210
Let those bad things go.

59
00:05:54,230 --> 00:05:56,320
Say goodbye to those old earrings.

60
00:05:56,980 --> 00:05:58,310
Put on these new earrings.

61
00:05:58,310 --> 00:06:00,510
It's all a new beginning.

62
00:06:01,780 --> 00:06:02,510
Don't worry.

63
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:04,630
I went to Qingfeng Restaurant today.

64
00:06:04,630 --> 00:06:06,660
I've figured out how to deal with her,

65
00:06:06,660 --> 00:06:09,120
so she'll drop to her knees and beg
for mercy.

66
00:06:09,270 --> 00:06:10,070
Shaoyi,

67
00:06:10,410 --> 00:06:11,930
you're doing this for me.

68
00:06:12,090 --> 00:06:13,410
Will Duan Yu be upset

69
00:06:13,690 --> 00:06:14,980
when he come back?

70
00:06:15,110 --> 00:06:15,870
I'm not doing this

71
00:06:15,870 --> 00:06:16,920
entirely for you,

72
00:06:17,340 --> 00:06:19,000
It's also for the Duan family.

73
00:06:19,250 --> 00:06:20,530
I want to know

74
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:22,590
why that girl deserve Duan Yu.

75
00:06:23,850 --> 00:06:25,710
If she couldn't even handle this,

76
00:06:26,110 --> 00:06:28,370
how could she marry into the Duan family?

77
00:06:30,470 --> 00:06:31,870
Show me the account book.

78
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:32,570
My Lady,

79
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:33,780
please review.

80
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:40,230
The business hasn't seen much improvement.

81
00:06:40,230 --> 00:06:42,290
We need to come up with something new.

82
00:06:46,310 --> 00:06:49,040
People are paying for the private room every day.

83
00:06:49,230 --> 00:06:50,810
It's under Du Ruoyun's name.

84
00:06:50,810 --> 00:06:53,020
Yes, it was from Young Master Shaoyi.

85
00:06:53,190 --> 00:06:54,720
He has booked it for three days.

86
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:56,620
He said he had something important

87
00:06:56,620 --> 00:06:57,700
to discuss in there.

88
00:06:57,700 --> 00:06:58,880
I don't understand the reason.

89
00:06:58,880 --> 00:06:59,909
How could you not understand?

90
00:06:59,909 --> 00:07:01,500
He knew our business wasn't doing well,

91
00:07:01,500 --> 00:07:02,720
so he wanted to help us.

92
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:03,990
He thought that I could lose face,

93
00:07:03,990 --> 00:07:05,190
so he came up with an excuse.

94
00:07:05,190 --> 00:07:07,100
That's what you call being a friend.

95
00:07:07,100 --> 00:07:08,030
Watch and learn.

96
00:07:08,870 --> 00:07:09,930
I'll go take a look.

97
00:07:13,710 --> 00:07:14,770
What are you doing?

98
00:07:15,150 --> 00:07:16,310
You can't come in.

99
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:18,550
This is strange.

100
00:07:18,590 --> 00:07:20,110
This is a private room in my restaurant.

101
00:07:20,110 --> 00:07:21,110
Why can't I enter?

102
00:07:25,090 --> 00:07:26,180
I booked it.

103
00:07:26,210 --> 00:07:27,070
You can't go in.

104
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:29,760
What are you doing here?

105
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:30,710
You're not doing anything

106
00:07:30,710 --> 00:07:32,060
shameful, are you?

107
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:34,630
Are you dating someone

108
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:35,810
in my private room?

109
00:07:36,470 --> 00:07:37,310
No.

110
00:07:37,330 --> 00:07:39,450
I have something important to do the day
after tomorrow.

111
00:07:39,450 --> 00:07:41,490
You'll find out by then.

112
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:42,930
But before that,

113
00:07:43,030 --> 00:07:44,030
you cannot enter.

114
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,350
Not only you are not permitted,

115
00:07:46,350 --> 00:07:48,750
none of your people are permitted to enter.

116
00:07:53,050 --> 00:07:54,570
So mysterious.

117
00:08:05,150 --> 00:08:05,950
Si.

118
00:08:08,270 --> 00:08:09,110
Miss Gu.

119
00:08:09,400 --> 00:08:10,600
What brings you here?

120
00:08:10,650 --> 00:08:11,560
Young Master has not come back yet.

121
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,360
I know.

122
00:08:12,690 --> 00:08:14,420
I just had something to ask you.

123
00:08:14,810 --> 00:08:16,630
Is the day after tomorrow an important day?

124
00:08:16,630 --> 00:08:17,960
The day after tomorrow?

125
00:08:18,780 --> 00:08:20,490
I... I don't think so.

126
00:08:21,260 --> 00:08:22,230
Is it possible

127
00:08:22,450 --> 00:08:23,910
that Duan Yu is coming back?

128
00:08:23,910 --> 00:08:25,050
I don't think it's that soon.

129
00:08:25,050 --> 00:08:27,450
Young Master will need some time to return.

130
00:08:28,410 --> 00:08:29,820
What day is it?

131
00:08:31,230 --> 00:08:32,390
Help me brainstorm

132
00:08:32,419 --> 00:08:33,610
things about Shaoyi.

133
00:08:33,610 --> 00:08:34,929
Young Master Shaoyi.

134
00:08:38,549 --> 00:08:39,380
I got it.

135
00:08:42,510 --> 00:08:43,309
I'm sorry.

136
00:08:43,510 --> 00:08:45,630
I am aware of what will happen tomorrow.

137
00:08:45,630 --> 00:08:46,640
Don't blame me for breaking my promise.

138
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:47,500
I'm barging in.

139
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:55,550
Duan Shaoyi, you scared me to death.

140
00:08:56,510 --> 00:08:59,150
This will be Gu Qingqiao's reaction tomorrow.

141
00:08:59,390 --> 00:09:00,590
When she goes in,

142
00:09:00,870 --> 00:09:03,400
she is going to step on the special oil
and slip.

143
00:09:03,400 --> 00:09:05,260
She'll fall down beside the table.

144
00:09:05,260 --> 00:09:07,160
There's a dangerous string.

145
00:09:07,730 --> 00:09:10,690
The string will cause the table to flip.

146
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:12,440
She won't know

147
00:09:12,460 --> 00:09:14,460
what will be waiting for her...

148
00:09:21,980 --> 00:09:23,150
When the moment comes,

149
00:09:23,150 --> 00:09:24,910
she and her Qingfeng Restaurant will become

150
00:09:24,910 --> 00:09:27,390
a laughingstock among the Changqing people.

151
00:09:27,390 --> 00:09:29,590
But are we pushing

152
00:09:29,610 --> 00:09:30,940
the boundaries too far?

153
00:09:31,170 --> 00:09:32,930
She'll get hurt if she falls.

154
00:09:33,550 --> 00:09:34,380
Don't worry.

155
00:09:34,590 --> 00:09:36,780
I've placed a water tank downstairs.

156
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,630
Even if she falls over,

157
00:09:38,660 --> 00:09:40,640
it will only be some scratches.

158
00:09:40,660 --> 00:09:41,520
She'll be safe.

159
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:42,640
But...

160
00:09:42,860 --> 00:09:43,950
then she will realize that

161
00:09:43,950 --> 00:09:46,660
she shouldn't have asked the storyteller to
defame you.

162
00:09:46,660 --> 00:09:47,320
Otherwise,

163
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:49,270
I'll keep messing with her,

164
00:09:49,270 --> 00:09:51,070
until she realizes her mistake.

165
00:09:52,670 --> 00:09:55,030
I'm teaching her a lesson for Duan Yu.

166
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,440
Young Master Shaoyi.

167
00:10:02,070 --> 00:10:02,970
Where is Gu Qingqiao?

168
00:10:02,970 --> 00:10:03,630
I don't know.

169
00:10:03,630 --> 00:10:05,320
I haven't seen her today.

170
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:09,150
Continue with your work.

171
00:10:15,910 --> 00:10:17,170
Why isn't she here yet?

172
00:10:18,560 --> 00:10:19,380
Duan Shaoyi.

173
00:10:20,770 --> 00:10:21,750
Gu Qingqiao.

174
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,330
Why are you in there?

175
00:10:36,410 --> 00:10:37,680
[Yong'an Street]

176
00:10:58,520 --> 00:11:00,880
[Birthday]

177
00:11:00,270 --> 00:11:00,950
Shaoyi.

178
00:11:00,990 --> 00:11:02,280
Happy birthday.

179
00:11:02,310 --> 00:11:03,460
Your idea of the trick room

180
00:11:03,460 --> 00:11:04,670
is amazing.

181
00:11:04,860 --> 00:11:06,950
It will definitely work in Qingfeng
Restaurant.

182
00:11:06,950 --> 00:11:08,110
I didn't expect you would prepare

183
00:11:08,110 --> 00:11:09,660
a big surprise for me on your birthday.

184
00:11:09,660 --> 00:11:10,790
Thank you.

185
00:11:11,750 --> 00:11:13,240
We've rehearsed for so many days.

186
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:15,180
Let's show it to Young Master Shaoyi.

187
00:11:15,180 --> 00:11:15,910
OK.

188
00:11:15,950 --> 00:11:17,230
One, two, three.

189
00:11:17,550 --> 00:11:20,420
Happy birthday to you.

190
00:11:20,590 --> 00:11:23,470
Happy birthday to you.

191
00:11:23,550 --> 00:11:26,750
Happy birthday to you.

192
00:11:26,790 --> 00:11:30,070
Happy birthday to you.

193
00:11:27,010 --> 00:11:29,770
[Birthday]

194
00:11:31,430 --> 00:11:34,830
Happy birthday, Shaoyi.

195
00:11:35,490 --> 00:11:36,230
Really?

196
00:11:36,250 --> 00:11:37,510
It's absolutely true.

197
00:11:37,550 --> 00:11:39,420
Qingfeng Restaurant is very popular these
days.

198
00:11:39,420 --> 00:11:41,660
It is said that many people booked this
room.

199
00:11:41,660 --> 00:11:44,060
Even more people are walking on the street.

200
00:11:44,140 --> 00:11:45,770
They are either here to have fun,

201
00:11:45,770 --> 00:11:47,430
or to collect candies.

202
00:11:47,990 --> 00:11:50,550
Gu Qingqiao is really extraordinary.

203
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:52,480
She is able to overcome

204
00:11:52,620 --> 00:11:54,080
any difficulty she faces.

205
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,030
When did you start

206
00:11:56,030 --> 00:11:57,960
keeping in touch with Gu Qingqiao?

207
00:11:58,430 --> 00:12:00,990
How could you not tell me about your secret
plan?

208
00:12:00,990 --> 00:12:03,510
I have never met Miss Gu.

209
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:05,940
I only found out today

210
00:12:05,970 --> 00:12:07,790
when she asked Si to host it.

211
00:12:07,820 --> 00:12:10,120
It's Si who's been arranging all this.

212
00:12:10,940 --> 00:12:13,210
It was meant to be a surprise,

213
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:14,530
so I didn't tell you.

214
00:12:16,620 --> 00:12:19,110
It was so embarrassing for me today.

215
00:12:19,470 --> 00:12:20,070
Not at all.

216
00:12:20,100 --> 00:12:21,600
We were all very touched.

217
00:12:22,030 --> 00:12:23,190
Today, I saw

218
00:12:23,210 --> 00:12:25,020
Si's eyes became watery.

219
00:12:27,330 --> 00:12:30,410
It seems there'a reason for Duan Yu to like
her.

220
00:12:31,100 --> 00:12:31,860
Well,

221
00:12:32,780 --> 00:12:33,980
About that...

222
00:12:34,230 --> 00:12:35,490
It'll be the last time.

223
00:12:38,420 --> 00:12:39,350
Duan Yu.

224
00:12:40,030 --> 00:12:42,910
I don't know how you're doing.

225
00:12:44,160 --> 00:12:45,410
Do you miss me?

226
00:12:46,510 --> 00:12:48,590
Anyway, I miss you so much.

227
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:52,920
Shaoyi has been really naughty.

228
00:12:53,940 --> 00:12:55,470
During your time away,

229
00:12:55,710 --> 00:12:57,750
he tries to trick me every day.

230
00:12:58,880 --> 00:13:01,490
I can only do my best

231
00:13:01,750 --> 00:13:03,230
to prevent it.

232
00:13:06,660 --> 00:13:09,900
I hope you can come back home safely.

233
00:13:23,810 --> 00:13:24,930
Duan Yu.

234
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:27,030
You're awake.

235
00:13:32,230 --> 00:13:33,110
May I ask.

236
00:13:33,670 --> 00:13:35,800
Are you the Lord of the Divine Palace?

237
00:13:36,040 --> 00:13:36,830
Yes.

238
00:13:37,040 --> 00:13:38,400
And no.

239
00:13:41,210 --> 00:13:42,300
Am I still

240
00:13:43,030 --> 00:13:44,190
in the Divine Palace?

241
00:13:44,190 --> 00:13:45,110
Yes.

242
00:13:45,290 --> 00:13:46,730
And no.

243
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:52,040
Does it mean

244
00:13:54,380 --> 00:13:55,570
I am dead?

245
00:13:55,710 --> 00:13:58,430
Life and death are unpredictable.

246
00:13:58,790 --> 00:14:02,250
Only faith is eternal.

247
00:14:02,340 --> 00:14:04,610
Then how did I get here?

248
00:14:05,190 --> 00:14:09,290
Divine Palace exists beyond the secular
world.

249
00:14:10,020 --> 00:14:14,400
It can't be invaded by any external force
or evil energy.

250
00:14:14,560 --> 00:14:15,910
If you want to get in,

251
00:14:16,550 --> 00:14:20,970
it depends on your own fate and ability.

252
00:14:21,570 --> 00:14:23,440
The stronger you are,

253
00:14:23,500 --> 00:14:25,130
the harder it is to get in.

254
00:14:25,340 --> 00:14:26,260
So, everything

255
00:14:26,450 --> 00:14:29,330
you encountered on your way in

256
00:14:29,370 --> 00:14:31,900
is set to minimize your ability

257
00:14:31,930 --> 00:14:35,650
to hurt the Divine Palace.

258
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:38,560
If you can see me,

259
00:14:38,950 --> 00:14:42,520
it proves that you have strong willpower.

260
00:14:43,710 --> 00:14:45,440
If you have any questions,

261
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:47,160
just ask.

262
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:50,080
The Star of Rebellion you predicted years
ago

263
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:51,280
has indeed appeared.

264
00:14:51,510 --> 00:14:53,430
I want to know if she poses

265
00:14:53,640 --> 00:14:55,350
a significant threat to the Duan family.

266
00:14:55,350 --> 00:14:58,750
If you didn't consider the threat
significant,

267
00:14:58,990 --> 00:15:01,330
you wouldn't have approach me.

268
00:15:01,530 --> 00:15:02,920
Is that correct?

269
00:15:03,260 --> 00:15:04,860
Is there a a win-win solution

270
00:15:05,140 --> 00:15:06,700
for her and the Duan family?

271
00:15:07,020 --> 00:15:08,530
Love and hatred

272
00:15:09,010 --> 00:15:11,210
are all part of your destiny.

273
00:15:11,940 --> 00:15:15,340
I'm willing to dedicate my life to reversing
her misfortune.

274
00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:20,390
If it's a misfortune, how can it be easily
resolved?

275
00:15:21,470 --> 00:15:26,360
Since you accessed the Divine Palace
with a strong will,

276
00:15:26,760 --> 00:15:31,440
why don't you use the power to foresee
the vision?

277
00:16:48,760 --> 00:16:49,640
Qiao.

278
00:16:52,550 --> 00:16:54,390
No.

279
00:17:03,700 --> 00:17:04,510
Qiao.

280
00:17:05,780 --> 00:17:06,890
Hang in there.

281
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:11,990
You really are my destiny.

282
00:17:12,940 --> 00:17:14,020
Goodbye.

283
00:17:15,950 --> 00:17:16,869
Qiao

284
00:17:17,750 --> 00:17:18,510
Duan Yu.

285
00:17:18,550 --> 00:17:19,750
No!

286
00:17:19,890 --> 00:17:20,560
