Bad news!

578
00:28:30,910 --> 00:28:32,870
What happened?

579
00:28:33,890 --> 00:28:37,250
Duan Shaoyi was kidnapped by Gu Qingqiao.

580
00:28:37,510 --> 00:28:39,360
Did you receive the letter too?

581
00:28:39,650 --> 00:28:40,680
Magistrate Du,

582
00:28:40,790 --> 00:28:42,250
the letter is fabricated.

583
00:28:42,270 --> 00:28:44,470
You really are something this time.

584
00:28:44,890 --> 00:28:46,810
Even you knew about this?

585
00:28:46,870 --> 00:28:48,250
What do you mean?

586
00:28:48,630 --> 00:28:49,870
What letter is fabricated?

587
00:28:49,870 --> 00:28:51,070
Don't talk nonsense.

588
00:28:51,950 --> 00:28:52,480
Mr. Du.

589
00:28:52,510 --> 00:28:53,970
The letter is fabricated.

590
00:28:54,640 --> 00:28:56,730
Here's the story.

591
00:28:56,920 --> 00:28:58,600
Young Master Shaoyi wanted to hire

592
00:28:58,600 --> 00:29:00,930
someone to pretend to kidnap Gu Qingqiao.

593
00:29:00,940 --> 00:29:02,220
It was all a joke.

594
00:29:02,950 --> 00:29:04,570
But he never thought

595
00:29:04,600 --> 00:29:06,330
the real kidnapper would come.

596
00:29:07,260 --> 00:29:09,040
I saw it with my own eyes.

597
00:29:09,270 --> 00:29:11,180
Gu Qingqiao colluded with the Mantra Sect

598
00:29:11,180 --> 00:29:12,950
to kidnap Young Master Shaoyi.

599
00:29:12,970 --> 00:29:13,770
What?

600
00:29:16,240 --> 00:29:18,110
The weather is so unreliable.

601
00:29:18,130 --> 00:29:19,320
It changes so quickly.

602
00:29:19,320 --> 00:29:22,720
I've long heard that your Four Pillars of
Destiny was cursed.

603
00:29:22,760 --> 00:29:24,980
People who meet you will have bad luck.

604
00:29:25,500 --> 00:29:26,640
No, I'm not.

605
00:29:34,290 --> 00:29:35,780
I'm not walking.

606
00:29:36,510 --> 00:29:37,510
I'm not walking.

607
00:29:41,360 --> 00:29:42,110
Sir,

608
00:29:42,730 --> 00:29:44,170
we only want this girl.

609
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:45,530
The guy is such a burden.

610
00:29:45,700 --> 00:29:47,160
I think we should kill him.

611
00:29:47,220 --> 00:29:49,350
That way, we'll be able to walk faster.

612
00:29:49,640 --> 00:29:50,130
Do it.

613
00:29:54,260 --> 00:29:55,240
Don't come over!

614
00:29:55,310 --> 00:29:57,640
If you dare lay a hand on him, I'll kill you!

615
00:29:58,340 --> 00:29:59,470
How dare you kill me?

616
00:29:59,760 --> 00:30:01,190
Do you know who my father is?

617
00:30:01,190 --> 00:30:03,250
My father is Duan Yan from Changqing.

618
00:30:03,320 --> 00:30:04,890
If you dare lay a finger on us,

619
00:30:04,890 --> 00:30:07,100
my father will kill you all.

620
00:30:08,460 --> 00:30:09,860
You're Duan Yan's son?

621
00:30:58,440 --> 00:30:59,460
Excuse me.

622
00:30:59,490 --> 00:31:01,570
Where is the nearby rest stop?

623
00:31:01,590 --> 00:31:02,460
I've been traveling for a long time.

624
00:31:02,460 --> 00:31:03,590
I want to take a rest.

625
00:31:03,730 --> 00:31:04,550
A rest stop?

626
00:31:05,170 --> 00:31:06,330
I don't know.

627
00:31:06,370 --> 00:31:07,790
I was just passing by.

628
00:31:08,510 --> 00:31:09,230
Are you also passing by?

629
00:31:09,230 --> 00:31:09,740
Yes.

630
00:31:09,910 --> 00:31:11,970
You didn't bring anything with you.

631
00:31:12,190 --> 00:31:13,650
You only have a good horse.

632
00:31:13,870 --> 00:31:16,120
I thought you were a local.

633
00:31:16,590 --> 00:31:17,630
Local?

634
00:31:18,390 --> 00:31:20,500
I'm just a traveler with a horse.

635
00:31:20,870 --> 00:31:21,780
Everywhere is my home.

636
00:31:21,780 --> 00:31:24,400
You must have a good horse when travelling.

637
00:31:24,650 --> 00:31:26,710
Money and clothes don't matter.

638
00:31:26,730 --> 00:31:27,400
Stop!

639
00:31:28,590 --> 00:31:30,120
What about people's lives?

640
00:31:30,290 --> 00:31:31,750
Do they not matter as well?

641
00:31:31,850 --> 00:31:32,720
Sir,

642
00:31:33,040 --> 00:31:34,570
what are you talking about?

643
00:31:34,880 --> 00:31:36,440
The horseshoes are new.

644
00:31:37,420 --> 00:31:39,220
If you're not a local,

645
00:31:39,300 --> 00:31:41,560
your horse must be new as well.

646
00:31:42,660 --> 00:31:43,750
The place

647
00:31:43,780 --> 00:31:45,380
that allows you to buy horses

648
00:31:45,450 --> 00:31:47,250
is the rest stop five miles away.

649
00:31:47,530 --> 00:31:48,660
Who are you?

650
00:31:49,540 --> 00:31:50,470
What do you want?

651
00:31:50,570 --> 00:31:53,430
I should be asking you that.

652
00:31:53,940 --> 00:31:56,300
Five people died at the rest stop.

653
00:31:58,030 --> 00:31:59,340
You're here for revenge,

654
00:31:59,340 --> 00:32:00,710
aren't you?

655
00:32:19,430 --> 00:32:20,520
You're quite good.

656
00:32:20,750 --> 00:32:22,090
No matter who you are,

657
00:32:22,120 --> 00:32:24,440
it's unfortunate of you to meet me today.

658
00:32:24,640 --> 00:32:26,480
I'm going to kill you too.

659
00:32:31,200 --> 00:32:32,190
Bloodcraft.

660
00:33:15,710 --> 00:33:16,260
Sir.

661
00:33:16,330 --> 00:33:17,330
Sorry we're late.

662
00:33:17,350 --> 00:33:18,040
It's okay.

663
00:33:18,540 --> 00:33:20,400
It was too sudden. Not your fault.

664
00:33:21,140 --> 00:33:22,360
How's the investigation going?

665
00:33:22,360 --> 00:33:23,290
Sir,

666
00:33:23,320 --> 00:33:24,540
we investigated the nearby villages.

667
00:33:24,540 --> 00:33:26,380
Everything seems fine. Nothing is wrong.

668
00:33:26,380 --> 00:33:28,780
It seems that this is not a simple incident.

669
00:33:28,930 --> 00:33:30,190
I have to report it to His Lordship as
soon as possible.

670
00:33:30,190 --> 00:33:31,680
Take care of this.

671
00:33:31,940 --> 00:33:32,420
Yes sir.

672
00:33:37,340 --> 00:33:42,050
[Duan Residence]

673
00:33:52,580 --> 00:33:53,650
Bastard!

674
00:33:53,990 --> 00:33:55,520
How did you protect Shaoyi?

675
00:33:56,110 --> 00:33:57,240
Shaoyi is immature.

676
00:33:57,260 --> 00:33:58,460
You too?

677
00:33:58,640 --> 00:33:59,580
So many people

678
00:33:59,600 --> 00:34:01,510
were fooled by a kid.

679
00:34:01,540 --> 00:34:02,650
His Lordship, please don't be angry.

680
00:34:02,650 --> 00:34:03,340
Mr. Qi

681
00:34:03,390 --> 00:34:05,390
has led Ruoyi in the search for them.

682
00:34:05,630 --> 00:34:07,810
It's my fault.

683
00:34:07,840 --> 00:34:08,730
Xing Si.

684
00:34:08,800 --> 00:34:09,710
You grew up

685
00:34:09,750 --> 00:34:11,580
in the Duan Residence.

686
00:34:12,120 --> 00:34:13,500
I am disappointed in you.

687
00:34:13,500 --> 00:34:14,420
I'm sorry.

688
00:34:15,199 --> 00:34:16,940
I will definitely find Young Master.

689
00:34:16,940 --> 00:34:18,150
If Shaoyi is fine,

690
00:34:18,270 --> 00:34:19,670
everything is fine.

691
00:34:19,940 --> 00:34:21,500
But if anything happens to Shaoyi,

692
00:34:21,500 --> 00:34:23,520
you and Wuyi Guards will be buried together.

693
00:34:23,520 --> 00:34:24,580
Yes, His Lordship.

694
00:34:25,500 --> 00:34:27,260
Ask Magistrate Du to come here immediately.

695
00:34:27,260 --> 00:34:28,520
I need to know everything.

696
00:34:28,520 --> 00:34:29,080
Yes.

697
00:34:36,600 --> 00:34:37,489
Xing Si.

698
00:34:37,830 --> 00:34:39,420
I heard that Mr. Duan is back.

699
00:34:39,420 --> 00:34:40,110
Yes.

700
00:34:40,420 --> 00:34:41,560
He was furious.

701
00:34:41,909 --> 00:34:44,380
He asked me to tell Magistrate Du to come
here to discuss something important.

702
00:34:44,380 --> 00:34:45,370
Shaoyi.

703
00:34:46,100 --> 00:34:47,550
Will Shaoyi be alright?

704
00:34:48,270 --> 00:34:49,480
Young Master Shaoyi is so smart.

705
00:34:49,480 --> 00:34:50,480
He will be fine.

706
00:34:50,800 --> 00:34:52,100
We have so many guards.

707
00:34:52,350 --> 00:34:54,170
Those kidnappers won't get too far.

708
00:34:54,170 --> 00:34:55,370
We'll find them soon.

709
00:34:56,510 --> 00:34:57,510
It's all my fault.

710
00:34:57,920 --> 00:34:59,930
If it wasn't for me,

711
00:35:00,080 --> 00:35:01,710
Shaoyi wouldn't have thought of pretending
to be kidnapped

712
00:35:01,710 --> 00:35:03,150
and framing Gu Qingqiao.

713
00:35:03,170 --> 00:35:04,800
If it wasn't to frame Gu Qingqiao,

714
00:35:04,800 --> 00:35:06,980
he wouldn't have gone to the wilderness.

715
00:35:06,980 --> 00:35:08,840
If he didn't go to the wilderness,

716
00:35:09,090 --> 00:35:11,210
he wouldn't have been kidnapped by the
Mantra Sect.

717
00:35:11,210 --> 00:35:11,970
Miss Du,

718
00:35:13,230 --> 00:35:14,490
everyone has his own fate.

719
00:35:14,490 --> 00:35:15,820
You can't blame others.

720
00:35:15,930 --> 00:35:17,630
What do you mean?

721
00:35:17,650 --> 00:35:19,470
No, I mean

722
00:35:19,500 --> 00:35:21,130
Young Master Shaoyi is blessed.

723
00:35:21,130 --> 00:35:22,890
I'm sure it'll turn out all right.

724
00:35:22,890 --> 00:35:23,760
Miss Du,

725
00:35:24,060 --> 00:35:25,320
don't blame yourself.

726
00:35:26,100 --> 00:35:27,500
If there's an option,

727
00:35:28,390 --> 00:35:29,960
I'd rather be the one being kidnapped.

728
00:35:29,960 --> 00:35:30,540
No.

729
00:35:32,410 --> 00:35:33,630
I mean

730
00:35:33,650 --> 00:35:35,260
nobody should be kidnapped.

731
00:35:35,590 --> 00:35:38,210
I won't let this happen again.

732
00:35:38,940 --> 00:35:39,810
Ruoyun.

733
00:35:40,630 --> 00:35:42,690
Don't go anywhere for the time being.

734
00:35:43,050 --> 00:35:44,560
Stay at home.

735
00:35:44,600 --> 00:35:45,520
It's safer.

736
00:35:46,240 --> 00:35:47,120
Guard Xing.

737
00:35:47,150 --> 00:35:48,110
Let's go.

738
00:35:48,520 --> 00:35:48,990
Yes.

739
00:35:51,160 --> 00:35:52,090
Shaoyi.

740
00:35:52,330 --> 00:35:54,190
Why aren't you saying something?

741
00:35:54,420 --> 00:35:56,320
Is your brain damaged?

742
00:35:57,150 --> 00:35:58,110
I'm fine.

743
00:35:58,710 --> 00:36:00,580
I feel they broke my neck.

744
00:36:01,110 --> 00:36:03,730
Why did they hit me so hard?

745
00:36:04,040 --> 00:36:06,240
This is my first time being knocked out.

746
00:36:06,560 --> 00:36:07,530
Are you okay?

747
00:36:07,630 --> 00:36:08,470
I'm fine.

748
00:36:08,900 --> 00:36:10,730
I'm better than you at fighting.

749
00:36:11,300 --> 00:36:12,260
Fighting?

750
00:36:12,540 --> 00:36:14,100
We were beaten.

751
00:36:14,700 --> 00:36:17,030
Even if we were beaten, I'd been stronger.

752
00:36:17,150 --> 00:36:19,430
I was born a Hercules.

753
00:36:19,460 --> 00:36:20,840
I'm stronger than many guys.

754
00:36:20,840 --> 00:36:23,140
I was the torch carrier in my neighborhood.

755
00:36:23,140 --> 00:36:24,900
I've even made a name for myself.

756
00:36:24,900 --> 00:36:26,230
What's a torch carrier?

757
00:36:26,750 --> 00:36:28,720
Why haven't I heard of your name?

758
00:36:28,980 --> 00:36:31,530
I didn't live in Changqing when I was young.

759
00:36:32,110 --> 00:36:33,580
Anyway, I'm fine.

760
00:36:35,020 --> 00:36:36,180
Look at you.

761
00:36:36,210 --> 00:36:38,870
How can an ancient man not know any
martial arts?

762
00:36:39,190 --> 00:36:41,110
If you had some strength,

763
00:36:41,140 --> 00:36:43,480
we wouldn't have ended up like this.

764
00:36:43,820 --> 00:36:45,230
Doesn't your family have

765
00:36:45,780 --> 00:36:47,600
a reputation in martial arts?

766
00:36:47,630 --> 00:36:50,190
We are now friends for life.

767
00:36:50,880 --> 00:36:52,290
To be honest,

768
00:36:52,710 --> 00:36:54,880
I don't have the talent for that.

769
00:36:55,040 --> 00:36:57,240
My father has hired many masters to train
me,

770
00:36:57,240 --> 00:36:58,370
but they all failed.

771
00:37:00,060 --> 00:37:01,070
That's good.

772
00:37:01,090 --> 00:37:02,090
Your body lacks coordination.

773
00:37:02,090 --> 00:37:03,050
That's so you.

774
00:37:03,190 --> 00:37:04,190
Don't laugh at me.

775
00:37:04,410 --> 00:37:05,090
If you laugh,

776
00:37:05,090 --> 00:37:06,700
I won't tell you anything anymore.

777
00:37:06,700 --> 00:37:07,390
I...

778
00:37:07,800 --> 00:37:09,640
I was just kidding.

779
00:37:10,110 --> 00:37:12,780
Actually, you're quite smart.

780
00:37:12,940 --> 00:37:14,010
You can use it.

781
00:37:14,100 --> 00:37:15,160
You got the talent.

782
00:37:15,270 --> 00:37:16,320
What's the point?

783
00:37:17,020 --> 00:37:19,610
I like to work on mechanisms.

784
00:37:19,640 --> 00:37:21,040
My father doesn't appreciate it at all.

785
00:37:21,040 --> 00:37:21,800
He says it's useless.

786
00:37:21,800 --> 00:37:23,060
I won't be successful.

787
00:37:23,060 --> 00:37:24,340
In this world,

788
00:37:24,790 --> 00:37:27,560
no one could define your success

789
00:37:27,850 --> 00:37:29,630
except for yourself.

790
00:37:29,790 --> 00:37:31,500
Only you could define your success.

791
00:37:31,500 --> 00:37:32,690
I think

792
00:37:33,060 --> 00:37:35,840
your mechanism is well designed.

793
00:37:36,110 --> 00:37:37,680
If you launch escape rooms

794
00:37:37,740 --> 00:37:39,070
in my place,

795
00:37:39,310 --> 00:37:40,340
you'll definitely get rich.

796
00:37:40,340 --> 00:37:41,510
What do you mean?

797
00:37:42,100 --> 00:37:42,900
I...

798
00:37:44,040 --> 00:37:47,150
I mean you helped Qingfeng Restaurant earn
a significant profit.

799
00:37:47,150 --> 00:37:48,330
You got the talent.

800
00:37:48,740 --> 00:37:49,800
I have faith in you.

801
00:37:50,400 --> 00:37:51,260
Come on.

802
00:37:51,290 --> 00:37:53,820
I can't do it just because you have faith
in me.

803
00:37:54,800 --> 00:37:56,060
You're a fast learner.

804
00:37:56,400 --> 00:37:57,400
You're talented.

805
00:37:58,120 --> 00:37:58,880
Sir,

806
00:37:58,920 --> 00:38:00,050
I don't understand.

807
00:38:00,580 --> 00:38:02,470
Why are we keeping that Duan guy?

808
00:38:02,810 --> 00:38:04,270
Why did we kidnap the girl?

809
00:38:04,390 --> 00:38:05,440
In order to find the relic.

810
00:38:05,440 --> 00:38:07,370
Where are we going to get the relic?

811
00:38:07,580 --> 00:38:08,390
The Right Guardian.

812
00:38:08,390 --> 00:38:10,320
Can you defeat the Right Guardian?

813
00:38:10,800 --> 00:38:11,920
No.

814
00:38:12,710 --> 00:38:14,770
But what does this have to do with him?

815
00:38:15,550 --> 00:38:17,510
Killing two birds with one stone, okay?

816
00:38:17,510 --> 00:38:20,110
Use Gu Qingqiao to lure out the Right Guardian.

817
00:38:20,170 --> 00:38:22,690
Use the Duan family to kill him.

818
00:38:22,720 --> 00:38:24,070
We can take back the relic

819
00:38:24,070 --> 00:38:25,800
without harming any of our men.

820
00:38:26,060 --> 00:38:28,210
But will the Right Guardian come?

821
00:38:29,190 --> 00:38:30,930
Back then at Qingfeng Restaurant,

822
00:38:30,930 --> 00:38:32,640
they worked together

823
00:38:32,670 --> 00:38:34,350
to kill many of our men.

824
00:38:34,600 --> 00:38:35,950
Their relationship

825
00:38:36,350 --> 00:38:37,810
is anything but ordinary.

826
00:38:38,140 --> 00:38:39,020
This time,

827
00:38:39,460 --> 00:38:42,590
I will make them pay with their blood.

828
00:38:43,640 --> 00:38:44,570
Tell me.

829
00:38:44,590 --> 00:38:45,930
Why did they kidnap you?

830
00:38:45,950 --> 00:38:48,500
They must be looking for something.

831
00:38:48,640 --> 00:38:49,660
What is it?

832
00:38:50,110 --> 00:38:51,220
Whose is it?

833
00:38:51,240 --> 00:38:52,720
This thing

834
00:38:53,110 --> 00:38:54,720
seems to be theirs,

835
00:38:54,750 --> 00:38:56,080
but it's actually mine.

836
00:38:56,650 --> 00:38:58,360
This is confusing.

837
00:38:58,550 --> 00:39:00,590
It's either theirs,

838
00:39:00,620 --> 00:39:02,190
or yours.

839
00:39:02,210 --> 00:39:05,050
How can it be theirs and yours?

840
00:39:06,660 --> 00:39:09,000
I can't explain it to you in a few words.

841
00:39:09,030 --> 00:39:11,270
I can't describe this thing to you.

842
00:39:11,290 --> 00:39:13,250
I don't have it on me now.

843
00:39:13,310 --> 00:39:14,020
It won't be easy

844
00:39:14,020 --> 00:39:15,480
for them to find it as well.

845
00:39:15,880 --> 00:39:17,520
I gave it to Duan Yu.

846
00:39:18,250 --> 00:39:19,600
Not bad.

847
00:39:22,880 --> 00:39:25,880
That's what Qingfeng Restaurant was about
last time?

848
00:39:26,610 --> 00:39:28,660
It's a pity that I did missed the fun.

849
00:39:29,210 --> 00:39:30,690
But it's good that you don't have it.

850
00:39:30,690 --> 00:39:32,130
If they found out,

851
00:39:32,140 --> 00:39:34,080
we would be dead by now.

852
00:39:34,100 --> 00:39:35,860
So smart of you.

853
00:39:36,150 --> 00:39:37,230
So,

854
00:39:37,410 --> 00:39:39,750
we have to use this information gap

855
00:39:39,780 --> 00:39:42,370
to find a way to escape.

856
00:39:42,610 --> 00:39:44,250
What's an information gap?

857
00:39:46,670 --> 00:39:49,630
An information gap is

858
00:39:50,660 --> 00:39:52,520
that they don't know what we know.

859
00:39:52,530 --> 00:39:54,540
We know everything they know.

860
00:39:54,580 --> 00:39:55,420
The part

861
00:39:55,420 --> 00:39:56,910
of knowing what they don't know

